features: 【Theme Style 60% Keyboard Gasket Mounted】 Womier V-K66 NEW multi-theme style mechanical keyboard, high quality and cost-effective design, is your best choice. The keyboard adopts gasket mounted structure with internal gasket design, pre-lubed linear switches, etc. Between the right FN key and the arrow keys, there are two indicator lights that make it simple to determine the Win/Mac mode and capitalization.

【Comfortable Typing Experience & Sound】This computer keyboard features a gasket structure with pre-lubed linear switch. It incorporates a transparent PC positioning board, internal gasket design, and a custom stabilizer keeps the big key from shaking. It's silky when typing and playing games, This design effectively reduces noise, resulting in a pure and comfortable typing experience with enhanced tactile feedback and sound quality.

【Popular Custom Keyboard】Users can quickly set up systems due to the convenience of the laser engraving hot-key side-print PBT keycaps. And these cherry profile backlit PBT keycaps are exceptionally durable to increase longevity. Additionally, This keyboard has a number of custom keycaps to cater for a variety of styles.

【LED Backlit Mini Keyboard & Macro Software】 Up to 19 LED lighting modes, you can freely choose the one compatible for the current using scenarios. With the superior macro software included with this wired mechanical keyboard, you can set the function of keyboard combination keys through editing software, so that the keyboard is more in line with your habits.

【Gaming keyboard Connection & Kickstand】 Wired connection with USB-C braided cable. Braided cable can extend longer service life and hard to rupture. Plug&Play. And it 2 gear height adjustment. You can change the different angle to suit you using needs. Anti-slip pad on the keyboard’s bottom guarantees that it doesn't rock back and forth when in use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars V-K66 different from K66
reviews.reviewText: Purchased on 9/28/23 while traveling for work. This version, the V-K66 was originally listed with the K66s like it was another less RGB in your face option. It was less than half the price of the acrylic K66s but I didn’t have much time to much about. Purchased and received quickly - which was great!This board however is not hotswap which was a bit disappointing as someone who likes to tinker but I purchased the linear reds and they are not offensive sounding the in the plastic case. RGB is definitely more offensive than any sound the board makes.You cannot turn off the RGB. I am all for a nice pastel slow rain drop or maybe a low steady light of one color. This board has neither other those things. I made the second mistake of purchasing PBT XDA pudding Keycaps because they were uniform and had the same quick shipping option. They sound pretty good on the board but holy RGB. Now that is mostly on me getting pudding Keycaps and the light is tamer with the included oem-ish Keycaps but my review photo is the pudding on steady light (only rainbow option is allowed) with the light turned alllll the way down so you to can to laugh at my horrification at the RGB monster I had accidentally bought and built.It uses the xvx wormier branded software/driver that must remain open at all times for any keep mapping/macros to work. This should be more apparent in the directions with the board or somewhere in the software. I am learning the hotkeys on the board as I do not want to keep the software/driver open.
